                            <td><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="harga-faq" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="700">
            <h3 class="faq-title">Pertanyaan Umum</h3>
            
            <div class="faq-container">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h4>Apakah saya bisa beralih paket kapan saja?</h4>
                        <span class="faq-icon"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Ya, Anda dapat beralih antar paket kapan saja. Jika Anda beralih ke paket yang lebih tinggi, perbedaan harga akan dihitung secara prorata. Jika Anda beralih ke paket yang lebih rendah, perubahan akan berlaku pada periode penagihan berikutnya.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h4>Bagaimana cara pembayaran untuk paket Premium?</h4>
                        <span class="faq-icon"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Kami menerima pembayaran melalui transfer bank, kartu kredit, dan e-wallet populer di Indonesia. Anda akan menerima invoice secara otomatis dan dapat melakukan pembayaran melalui metode yang Anda pilih.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h4>Apakah ada kontrak jangka panjang?</h4>
                        <span class="faq-icon"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Tidak ada kontrak jangka panjang yang mengikat. Anda dapat berlangganan bulanan atau tahunan, dan dapat membatalkan kapan saja. Untuk paket tahunan, Anda mendapatkan diskon 20% dibandingkan dengan pembayaran bulanan.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h4>Apakah data kami aman?</h4>
                        <span class="faq-icon"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Keamanan data adalah prioritas utama kami. Kami menggunakan enkripsi end-to-end, backup data reguler, dan mengikuti standar keamanan industri untuk memastikan data Anda selalu aman dan terlindungi.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="harga-cta" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="800">
            <div class="cta-content">
                <h3>Siap untuk meningkatkan manajemen komplek perumahan Anda?</h3>
                <p>Mulai dengan paket Gratis atau hubungi kami untuk konsultasi kebutuhan khusus Anda.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="cta-buttons">
                <a href="#" class="btn-harga btn-outline">Mulai Gratis</a>
                <a href="/kontak" class="btn-harga btn-primary">Hubungi Kami</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    /* Harga Section Styles */
    .harga-section {
        position: relative;
        padding: 120px 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        background-color: var(--bg-light);
        isolation: isolate;
    }

    /* Animated background elements */
    .harga-bg-elements {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        pointer-events: none;
        z-index: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .bg-element {
        position: absolute;
        border-radius: 50%;
        opacity: 0.05;
        filter: blur(40px);
    }
    
    .bg-element-1 {
        width: 400px;
        height: 400px;
        top: -150px;
        right: 10%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--primary-blue) 0%, transparent 70%);
        animation: float 20s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }
    
    .bg-element-2 {
        width: 300px;
        height: 300px;
        bottom: -100px;
        left: 5%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--muted-green) 0%, transparent 70%);
        animation: float 15s ease-in-out 5s infinite alternate-reverse;
    }
    
    .bg-element-3 {
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
        top: 30%;
        left: 20%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--muted-orange) 0%, transparent 70%);
        animation: pulse 10s ease-in-out infinite;
        opacity: 0.03;
    }
    
    .bg-element-4 {
        width: 250px;
        height: 250px;
        top: 40%;
        right: 15%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--primary-blue-light) 0%, transparent 70%);
        animation: pulse 12s ease-in-out 2s infinite alternate;
        opacity: 0.03;
    }

    .section-title {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: var(--text-dark);
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .section-subtitle {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto 3rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    /* Pricing Tabs */
    .harga-tabs {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        border-radius: 50px;
        padding: 0.5rem;
        width: fit-content;
        margin: 0 auto 3rem;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    }

    .tab-btn {
        padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
        border: none;
        background: transparent;
        color: var(--text-dark);
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .tab-btn.active {
        color: var(--white);
    }

    .tab-slider {
        position: absolute;
        height: 80%;
        top: 10%;
        left: 0.5rem;
        width: calc(50% - 1rem);
        background: var(--primary-blue);
        border-radius: 50px;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    /* Pricing Cards Container */
    .harga-container {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    /* Pricing Card */
    .harga-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
        position: relative;
        transition: all 0.4s var(--bounce);
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        height: 100%;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .harga-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-10px);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-color: rgba(var(--primary-blue-rgb), 0.3);
    }

    .harga-card.featured {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
        border-color: rgba(var(--primary-blue-rgb), 0.2);
        box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(var(--primary-blue-rgb), 0.15);
        transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .harga-card.featured:hover {
        transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(var(--primary-blue-rgb), 0.2);
    }

    .harga-card-badge {
        position: absolute;
        top: 1rem;
        right: -3rem;
        background: var(--primary-blue);
        color: var(--white);
        padding: 0.5rem 3rem;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        transform: rotate(45deg);
        box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(var(--primary-blue-rgb), 0.3);
    }

    .card-decoration {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        right: 0;
        width: 150px;
        height: 150px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(var(--primary-blue-rgb), 0.1), transparent);
        border-radius: 0 20px 0 100%;
        opacity: 0.5;
        transition: all 0.4s ease;
        z-index: -1;
    }

    .harga-card:hover .card-decoration {
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
        opacity: 0.7;
        transform: rotate(-5deg);
    }

    .card-glow {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: -50px;
        left: -50px;
        width: 100px;
        height: 100px;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(var(--primary-blue-rgb), 0.3) 0%, transparent 70%);
        border-radius: 50%;
        opacity: 0;
        transition: all 0.4s ease;
        z-index: -1;
        filter: blur(20px);
    }

    .harga-card:hover .card-glow {
        opacity: 0.7;
        width: 150px;
        height: 150px;
    }

    /* Card Header */
    .harga-card-header {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .harga-card-header h3 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: var(--text-dark);
    }

    .harga-price {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .price {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: var(--primary-blue);
    }

    .period {
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    /* Card Body */
    .harga-card-body {
        flex-grow: 1;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .harga-features {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .feature-item {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .feature-item:hover {
        transform: translateX(5px);
    }

    .feature-icon {
        margin-right: 1rem;
        color: var(--primary-blue);
        font-size: 1rem;
        padding-top: 0.2rem;
    }
    
    .feature-icon .fa-plus {
        color: var(--primary-blue);
    }

    .feature-item.disabled .feature-icon {
        color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .feature-text {
        color: var(--text-dark);
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
